{"tid":22293,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"一半價錢在 ZARA 買 adidas 「熱門鞋款」?","createTime":"2016-12-04T10:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T13:17:58.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43fa5c9bdc0fc1036d73a7f03afea220aee4bb48","tid":22293,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"其實ZARA雖然以較高的性價比活躍在商場內，但他的設計經常會抄襲一些大牌，比如 GIVENCHY、Chole 等等，也抄襲過侃爺的 Yeezy Season，後來又將抄襲魔抓伸向洛杉磯獨立藝術家 Tuesday Bassen，也讓一些網友覺得非常憤怒，因為所有設計都是設計師的心血，模仿與抄襲是對設計師的不尊重。<br />\n<br />\n而此番，ZARA再次向鞋履進軍，ZARA 今季最新的球鞋系列與多款 adidas 的大熱款式相似，包括女生大愛的 Superstar Slip-On；又或是混合上變色 XENO 材質、幾乎一樣的 Stan Smith「Black Reptile」；大熱跑鞋款式 Ultra Boost 外型的編織物料設計；還將Adidas最新主打產品 AlphaBOUNCE 混合 Puma RF-Blaze of Glory 進行創作，相當猖狂。大家怎麼看呢？反正我覺得這樣的抄襲跟莆田有什麼區別？<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/fashion/93rv28.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Ffashion%2F93rv28.html&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=edde171d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/fashion/93rv28.html</a>"},{"pid":"2224751f59d06f4f0ff7a0e81fe11d6426eae553","tid":22293,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/c4e0012580de9a4e0ba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fc4e0012580de9a4e0ba&h=af1c5682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/c50001259c02934233e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fc50001259c02934233e&h=3f96a066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/c420012f2f413f6b763\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fc420012f2f413f6b763&h=ce95e99d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/c4e0012580f89ebfa90\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kkn